WEBVTT

00:00:58.475 --> 00:01:00.345
invented in the 20th century:

00:01:00.369 --> 00:01:01.652
the steel pan.

00:01:02.318 --> 00:01:04.711
Deriving from the African drums

00:01:04.735 --> 00:01:08.012
and evolving from the genius
of one of the ghettos in Trinidad,

00:01:08.036 --> 00:01:09.722
a city called Laventille,

00:01:09.746 --> 00:01:12.722
and the disregard
of the American military ...

00:01:13.537 --> 00:01:14.833
Well, I should tell you,

00:01:14.857 --> 00:01:18.224
America, during WWII, had
military bases set up in Trinidad,

00:01:18.248 --> 00:01:19.669
and when the war ended,

00:01:19.693 --> 00:01:23.229
they left the island littered
with empty oil drums --

00:01:23.253 --> 00:01:24.498
their trash.

00:01:24.947 --> 00:01:29.231
So people from Laventille
repurposed the old drums left behind

